# Hello! What would you like to test?

We're just geting started! I want to walk you through the modules I've built for our team. 

The LRS will automatically store which link you choose on each passage. Open up your browser's console to see what's loaded, and that statements have been received. Please note that we are still working on interactivity, so the UX lacks some responsiveness. 

*Please note this site stores a cookie in your browser to log you as an Actor. We do not ant to collect any personal info!*

