:: Checkbox

# Check the box… Uncheck the box…
They will all be recorded, so don't click too frequently. 

    <label for="checkbox">Check me:</label>
    <input type="checkbox" id="checkbox">
    <i><p id="output"></p></i>

### Where to next?

- <span id="chooseButtonClick">[[Test a button click|Button Click]]</span>
- <span id="chooseMultipleChoice">[[Test a Multiple Choice Selection|Multiple Choice]]</span>
- <span id="chooseInput">[[Test a Single-Line Text Input|Single-Line Text]]</span>
- <span id="chooseTextArea">[[Test a  Multiline Text Input|Multiline Text]]</span>

<%
$(function () {
    const checkbox = document.getElementById('checkbox');
    const output = document.getElementById('output');
    function handleCheckboxChange(event) {
        if (event.target.checked) {
            s.checkbox = "Checked!";
            output.textContent = 'Checkbox is checked';
            send_checkbox();
        } else {
            s.checkbox = "Unchecked!";
            output.textContent = 'Checkbox is unchecked';
            send_checkbox();
        }
    }
    checkbox.addEventListener('change', handleCheckboxChange);
});
%>

